        "data": "<h1 id=\"01H8066N1X71BMWR8KPQVMTM4A\" class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n<p>The services update for 03/25/2025 is a minor update for <strong>Backup</strong> and patch update for <strong>CI </strong>and<strong> Database </strong>service.</p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1X678XQSM8P38E9Q5Z\">DXP Cloud Stack </h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 634px; height: 214px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2812px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.22.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.23.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\"><strong>liferaycloud/backup:5.23.0</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>CI</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">6.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>6.0.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\"><strong>liferaycloud/jenkins:2.479.3-lts-jdk21-6.0.1</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Database</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.6.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.6.3</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\"><strong>liferaycloud/database:5.6.3</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">Liferay</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.8.3</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2812px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.8.4</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.8.4</li>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.3-5.8.4</li>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.8.4</li>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.1-5.8.4</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.3.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2812px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.3.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:8.15.1-5.3.2</li>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:7.17.23-5.3.2</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Webserver</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">6.1.5</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">6.1.6</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 374.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/nginx:1.24.0-6.1.6</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YWTXV16JYNYMDV6F4\">Change Log</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto; height: 94px; width: 651px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 71.5179px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 62.8482px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 106.839px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket No.</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 366.938px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 71.5179px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>CI</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62.8482px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>6.0.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 106.839px; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-44976\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-44976</a></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 366.938px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Update Jenkins to 2.479.3-lts-jdk21</li>\n<li>Fix multiple CVEs</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 71.5179px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62.8482px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.23.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 106.839px; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-44596\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-44596</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-45196\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-45196</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-44975\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-44975</a></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 366.938px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<ul>\n<li>(GCS) Track Backup Creation leveraging status from GCS  </li>\n<li>Fix Multiple CVEs</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 71.5179px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Database</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62.8482px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.6.3</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 106.839px; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-44978\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-44978</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-45195\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-45195</a></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 366.938px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Fix multiple CVEs</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>Notes:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Listing some notable CVEs - </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>CVEs Fixed in CI</strong>  \n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://pkg.go.dev/vuln/GO-2024-2887\">CVE-2024-24790</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pkg.go.dev/vuln/GO-2023-1840\">CVE-2023-29403</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://osv.dev/vulnerability/GHSA-4374-p667-p6c8\">CVE-2023-39325</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pkg.go.dev/vuln/GO-2023-2375\">CVE-2023-45287</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pkg.go.dev/vuln/GO-2023-2186\">CVE-2023-45284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pkg.go.dev/vuln/GO-2023-2382\">CVE-2023-39326</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong><span>CVEs Fixed in Backup</span></strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-27152\"><span>CVE-2025-27152</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span></span><strong><span>CVEs Fixed in Database </span></strong>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span></span><a href=\"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-27152\"><span>CVE-2025-27152</span></a>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-968p-4wvh-cqc8\">CVE-2025-27789</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>A lot more CVEs were fixed with this release. If you need more information on that feel free to open a customer support ticket.</p>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HFQQE47127T9RVN8YK7MKH4R\">Update Instructions</h2>\n<p><strong>Note</strong><span> : To take advantage of the new features and fixes provided by the 5.x stack of services, you must update your entire stack to the new 5.x images or above.</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YDXGGCTPJ2C2XKQWE\">Image Update Instructions</h2>\n<p>The Liferay Cloud image versions needs to be set inside of the &lt;service&gt;/LCP.json file.</p>\n<p>Note, however, that the liferay service uses two image properties. The DXP Cloud image is set in the liferay/LCP.json file, but the liferay/dxp image is set in the gradle.properties. This change was made in order to facilitate easier deployment using the Liferay Cloud CLI.</p>\n<p>liferay/LCP.json file would set the liferaycloud/liferay-dxp image: </p>\n<pre><span>\"image\"</span>:<span>\"liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.X.X\"</span></pre>\n<p>liferay/gradle.properties file would set the liferay/dxp image:</p>\n<pre><span>liferay.workspace.docker.image.liferay</span>=<span>liferay/dxp:2024.q1.1</span><span></span></pre>\n<p>For all other images, you will just need to update the LCP.json file with the intended image version.</p>\n<p>Once the LCP.json files are updated, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n<pre>git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"Update dxp cloud stack to XXX\"</pre>\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>"
      },
